quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,17,"Munhu wese achapihwa zvaakawana nhasi. Nhasi hapana ari kuzodzvanyirirwa. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanokurumidza pakutonga"
  40,18,"Uye vayeuchidze (Muhammad (SAW)) nezve zuva iri riri kuswedera pedyo, apo moyo ichange iri pahuro, uye havasi kuzokwanisa kuidzosera (moyo) muzvipfuva kana kuibuditsa panze. Vaiita mabasa akaipa havasi kuzova neshamwari, kana vamiririri, vari kuzoteererwa"
  40,19,"Allah vanoziva kunyepa kwemaziso, uye nezvose zvinovigwa nezvipfuva"
  40,20,"Uye Allah vanotonga muchokwadi, asi avo vavanonamata kunze kwavo, hapana chavanokwanisa kutonga. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanonzwa zvese, vanoona zvese"
  40,21,"Havana here kufamba munyika vakaona magumo eavo vaivapo mushure mavo? Vaive pamusoro pavo pasimba uye matsimba (avakasiya) ari panyika. Asi Allah vakavaparadza nemurango nekuda kwezvitadzo zvavo, uye havana akavachengetedza kubva kuna Allah"
  40,22,"Izvi zvaiva, nokuti kwakauya kwavari vatumwa vavo nezviratidzo zviri pachena asi havana kutenda. Naizvozvo Allah vakavaparadza (nemutongo). Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vane simba rose, vane mutongo wakaomarara"
  40,23,"Uye zvirokwazvo takava tinotumira Musa nezviratidzo zvedu, uye nemutemo uri pachena (wakajekeswa)"
  40,24,"Kuna Farawo, Haamaan uye Qaaroon (Korah), asi vakamuti: “Muiti wemapipi, munyepi!”"
  40,25,"Nokudaro paakavaunzira chokwadi kubva kwatiri, vakati: “Urayai vanakomana veavo vanotenda pamwechete naye mova munosiya vanhukadzi vavo kuti vararame.” Asi urongwa hwevasingatendi hauna budiriro asi kurasikirwa"